entries.femaleVariant: How about the guy in number two? Shoulda heard him screaming last night.
How are you this fine day, your majesty? Is this treatment working? All those pieces in that little head fitting together?
Please, just leave me alone... Please, God...
Jesus Christ, another?! How much do you smoke? A pack a day?
Uh, the cloud of secondhand smoke? Take it outside!
All right, I'm going. Just cool your tits, OK?
Hmm, down in the dumps today, are we? We'll have to double your dose then. Or just go straight to lobotomy.
He spit out his tabs, so we gave it to him through the "other" end.
Now when we come in he's already got his tongue out.
